    "Section 4 introduces research in respect of video feature extraction, which is divided into traditional methods and deep learning methods.",
    "Video feature extraction must be introduced as a public step of video task processing.",
    "In this review we introduce feature extraction by means of CNN, RNN, and transformers.",
    "Section 5 introduces algorithms based on algorithm structure; these can be divided into three types according to the design methods: anchor-based, boundary-based and query-based.",
    "Section 6 introduces algorithms based on the supervision mode, focusing on weak supervision, and provides a general introduction to full supervision and no supervision."
